  <brief_title>Psychosocial Interventions in the Treatment of Youth With Type 1 Diabetes Mellitus</brief_title>
  <official_title>Intensive Individual and Familial Psychosocial Interventions in the Treatment of Children and Adolescents With Type 1 Diabetes Mellitus</official_title>
